chat.msg: hey there, estas listo?
si
sweet, let's crack this
i'm at the starting point, facing a twig leading to a tiny island with a tiger. should i head over this way?
yes right under the rock under the tiger
got it, walking past the tiger and now under the rock
i see another small island in the south-east with a butterfly. should i head there?
no go towards the island with the parrot and make your line go above the parrot and in the middle of the elephant going under the parrot again
alrighty then, heading towards the parrot island and going above the parrot, then under it in the middle of the elephant
on it, my friend
ok
now, just to the left there's our friend, the frog
do i go visit him?
yes go through the rock path that leads to the frog then make your line directly on the alligator
you got it, boss! i'm heading down the rock path to our froggy friend, then making a beeline for the crocodile
here goes nothing!
great
there's the elephant again to my left
should i pay another visit?
no instead make a line to the dark rock to the light Frey rock then under the feet of the giraffe
on it! going past the elephant, then from the dark rock to the light grey one, and then sneaking under the long legs of the giraffe
done and dusted!
now make your way through the water to the snake on the tree and then to the chest
i'm on it, swimming through the water to say hi to our slithery pal and then to that shiny chest!  *finished*

yes
awesome! okay, i'm chillin' by the tent up north
which way do i go first?
okay so go south, down in between the rock wall and the beagle looking dog

now, south or west next?
then go under the dog and up in between the cozy fire
alright, walked past the fire here
i see a red mushroom and a cool blue car. which way now?
once you are above the fire go in-between the bush and fire and under the mushroom

what's next?
from there go on the trail and over the bush next to the car then head south on the trail and then go in between the telescope and the bush
cool, i've gone south past the telescope
i can see some rocks and a wooden house. is this the right way?
yes once you have gone in between the telescope and bush go west under the rocks then on the rocks until you make it to the cabin

chat.msg: hola, q tal? ready to play?
yes
awesome! okay, let's start. first, there's a trio of palm trees near you, let's move to the first one to the south-west, and get under it
from there, turn right, cross the second palm tree, then make a sharp left before the third one, heading south. got it? cool! let's continue!
cool
good job! now, keep going until you see a cute brown puppy on your left
don't play with it though! move slightly left, then turn right heading south
ok
great! you’ll see a big rock on your left and a small one on your right, walk right between them till you reach the water
ready to get your feet wet?
yes
cool! you'll find a big red crab in the water, make a right turn here, wade along the big rock and keep moving west in the water
ok
good going! keep an eye out for a medium rock in the water
there's a shark past it but don't get scared! make a sharp right here
ok
solid! now back to dry land
cross between the medium rock and a multicolored ball, keep moving north. you're doing great!
ok
fantastic! now, veer slightly left, head northwest
you'll see a red tent and a large speaker – just keep going between them. how's everything so far?
great
awesome! now this part's fun
i want you to circle around the tent in an arc. it'll look like you're going back but trust me on this
ok
nice
now move towards the sea, just stop at the shore. take a right turn heading west below the red kayak
ok
way to go! make a sharp turn right along the kayak, heading north
you're almost there!
ok
fantastic! now, just move toward the small green bush near you
you've made it!
